udocker 1.0.0

 * Initial version

udocker 1.0.1

 * Minor bugfixes
 * Use udocker as executable name instead of udocker.py
 * Improve verbose levels and messaging
 * Support for login into docker repositories
 * Support for private repositories
 * Listing of v2 repositories catalog
 * Improve download handling for v1 and v2 repositories
 * Fix insecure flag to avoid validation of host certificates
 * Added checksum verification for sha256 layers
 * Address seccomp change introduced on kernels >= 4.8.8
 * Installation tarball structure improved
 * Utility to build binary executables and create a tarball
